title: Race Like A Girl
description: Track-style racing on the half-mile Union Park loop. Categories for Mens and Women's A and B, plus novice. Races will be short and each category will have the opportunity to race multiple times.
course: Held on a closed half-mile paved loop in Union Park in Des Moines. Start and finish located at south side of loop. Parking on park roads leading to loop.
registration: Registration $15. Onsite registration only. USAC annual or one-day license required. Register at tables near start/finish line. Registration opens at 4:30 on day of race. Closes 15 minutes prior to race start.
notes: Race series held on third Thursday in May, June, July and August. Race schedule will be posted at registration each night.
directions: Union Park is located off Pennsylvania Ave. north of University on Des Moines near east side.

title: Bicycle Blues and BBQ Omnium - Flyover MORS #5
description:
Bicycle, Blues and Barbeque Omnium Weekend
July 10-12, 2015
Clear Lake, IA 

The Bicycle, Blues and Barbeque Omnium Weekend is the best cash purse payout of the Flyover series at $15,500 including cash primes plus $3,500 in merchandise prizes!

 As a part of the Junior Devo Race Series the full range of junior ages both male and female will be scored: 9-12, 13-14, 15-16, 17-18.   
Please join us Friday night in City Park for the kickoff of the 2015 BBQ Blues Festival at 5:00pm.  All pre-registered riders will receive two complimentary beer tickets to the hospitality tent Friday night.  Further registration and race details are available here:  http://bicyclebluesbbq.com/
course:
TT: 7 miles out and back, riser going out. 
Crit: Fast Technical Course 
RR: 83 and 45 miles routes with rollers and wind. Note: P1,2's and 3's will be doing a circuit this year due to bridge construction.
registration: You must be pre-registered for the Time Trial as there are No Day of Registration for the TT.  Pre-Registraion Closes Thursday, July 9th at 10:00 p.m.
notes: By registering for the Omnium event on USA Cycling, you will automatically be entered into the TT, Criterium and Road Race events.  All races earn Omnium Points.  Please read race bible for complete event details.
